Product personalization ranking (option 1, query params)

Inputs (CSV, optional weight suffix ":N"):
- visited_categories
- visited_tags
- visited_brands
- visited_attributes (key=value or value)

Scoring (fixed weights):
- category match weight x3
- tag match weight x2
- brand match weight x2
- attribute match weight x1

Example:
/api/products?visited_categories=shoes:5,accessories:2&visited_attributes=color=black:3,size=xl
